<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.7">
<l>tiruvāḻmār vaṉṟaṉṉait ticaimaṇṇī  rerimutalā</l>
<l>vuruvāyniṉ ṟavaṉai yolicē rumārutattai</l>
<l>varuvāyniṉ ṟavaṉait teṉṉaḻuntaiyil maṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>karuvārkaṟ pakattaikkaṇ ṭukoṇṭuka ḷittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself the one at whose chest Tiru lives,</l>
<l>The one who endures becoming formed as the regions,</l>
<l rend="indent">earth, water, fire, and all,</l>
<l>The one who endures becoming unformed as the wind with its roar,</l>
<l>The kalpaka tree, which spreads dark [shade], and which stands eternally</l>
<l rend="indent">in Aḻuntai of the south, I was reeling!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
